org.jpedal.examples.viewer.gui.javafx.dialog

Class FXMessageDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpedal.examples.viewer.gui.javafx.dialog.FXDialog
      • org.jpedal.examples.viewer.gui.javafx.dialog.FXMessageDialog
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FXInputDialog, FXOptionDialog

    public class FXMessageDialog
extends FXDialog
    An extension of FXDialog which displays a message to the user. You can set an image as the warning image and the message text.
    Author:
    Simon
